this rich pageant

06:10.417 --> 06:13.667
without your good
and wise counsel.

06:13.667 --> 06:17.000
♪ dramatic music  ♪

06:17.000 --> 06:20.041
The deal goes out
at $18 dollars a share tomorrow.

06:20.041 --> 06:21.375
Holy shit!

06:21.375 --> 06:24.333
I'm worth
$125 million dollars.

06:24.333 --> 06:26.375
Yeah, you may well be
soon enough,

06:26.375 --> 06:28.542
but don't allow yourself
to feel it just yet.

06:28.542 --> 06:30.041
That clouds the thinking

06:30.041 --> 06:32.875
at the exact moment when
you need to be clear-headed.

06:32.875 --> 06:34.625
Is that
gonna clear my head?

06:34.625 --> 06:36.375
Hey, scotch this good,

06:36.375 --> 06:39.834
make a Mongoloid
think like Einstein.

06:39.834 --> 06:40.250
Oh, God, no.

06:40.250 --> 06:41.959
Jesus, Dad.

06:41.959 --> 06:43.917
We're in my house,
son.

06:43.917 --> 06:47.000
There will be no nod to this
Billie Jean King PC bullshit.

06:47.000 --> 06:48.583
It's just wrong, you know?
No.

06:48.583 --> 06:50.625
Some things are just
actually wrong.

06:50.625 --> 06:52.291
Ah...
You two, not tonight,

06:52.291 --> 06:54.583
not the night before
my IPO comes out.

06:54.583 --> 06:55.625
Quite so, Ira.

06:55.625 --> 06:56.792
Congratulations.

06:56.792 --> 06:58.500
Absolutely.
To that.

06:59.458 --> 07:00.750
I'm very happy
for you both that

07:00.750 --> 07:03.959
this venture's off to
such an auspicious start,

07:03.959 --> 07:06.750
but I do advise caution--
You brought us together.

07:06.750 --> 07:08.792
Whatever happens,
you share in it.

07:08.792 --> 07:10.291
Oh, I do.

07:10.291 --> 07:12.417
My emotions are
all tied up in it, for sure.

07:12.417 --> 07:15.208
When the market
closes tomorrow

07:15.208 --> 07:17.625
and we have ridden this thing
all the way up,

07:17.625 --> 07:19.917
that $125-million number
might be...

07:19.917 --> 07:22.000
conservative.

07:22.000 --> 07:23.542
Yes.

07:23.542 --> 07:25.708
Don't quit your day job.

07:25.708 --> 07:26.625
Too late.

07:27.875 --> 07:28.583
You didn't.

07:28.583 --> 07:30.542
Not all the way,
but close.

07:30.542 --> 07:35.000
I'm selling my share of the firm
to my partners.

07:35.000 --> 07:36.750
It's been
a long time coming.

07:36.750 --> 07:38.458
Tomorrow
is liberation day.

07:38.458 --> 07:40.708
You never tally your sheet
until the lockup period is over,

07:40.708 --> 07:44.083
but even I have to admit
it does feel great.

07:44.083 --> 07:45.959
You did
a good thing here, son.

07:45.959 --> 07:46.625
You absolutely did.

07:46.625 --> 07:49.291
I hope that's true,
Dad.

07:49.291 --> 07:53.500
I really do.

07:56.917 --> 07:58.375
Is this...

07:58.375 --> 07:59.291
Weird?

07:59.291 --> 08:03.834
I was gonna say
"feeling as right to you,"

08:03.834 --> 08:05.542
but, uh...

08:05.542 --> 08:07.750
Mm. Sorry.

08:07.750 --> 08:10.375
I mean making a habit of these
husband/wife booty calls.

08:10.375 --> 08:12.625
Oh. "Booty calls."

08:12.625 --> 08:17.041
I feel
I'm finally a man of my time.

08:24.417 --> 08:27.667
How do you think
I engineer a cup of Stumptown?

08:27.667 --> 08:30.291
Not by heading down
to the kitchen.

08:30.291 --> 08:31.834
You need to slip out
before the kids are up.

08:31.834 --> 08:35.917
It's not fair to give them
a false sense of hope.

08:35.917 --> 08:37.250
False?

08:37.250 --> 08:39.542
That's gonna leave a mark.

08:45.667 --> 08:47.458
You look like
my guys at work.

08:47.458 --> 08:48.625
What's so interesting?

08:48.625 --> 08:51.291
Pre-trading news
on the juice IPO,

08:51.291 --> 08:52.417
and it is good news.

08:52.417 --> 08:55.792
Oh, so exciting
for Ira.

08:58.708 --> 09:00.583
Not just  Ira.

09:00.583 --> 09:03.625
Nobody knows this,
not even Ira,

09:03.625 --> 09:06.625
but, uh...
I'm in it, too.

09:06.625 --> 09:08.208
In it?

09:08.208 --> 09:09.041
That's right.

09:09.041 --> 09:11.458
Why?

09:11.458 --> 09:13.250
'Cause it's a winner.

09:13.250 --> 09:15.667
And you know this
because...

09:15.667 --> 09:17.208
Because I saw it...

09:17.208 --> 09:19.500
exactly what would happen
with this company

09:19.500 --> 09:20.834
and what it would do
for me.

09:20.834 --> 09:26.000
I've only seen three things
that  clearly in my life.

09:26.000 --> 09:30.041
One was my first time
actually arguing in court.

09:30.041 --> 09:32.208
I knew
it was my calling.

09:32.208 --> 09:35.834
Second was
when I met you...

09:35.834 --> 09:39.542
and I knew
it was my destiny.

09:39.542 --> 09:41.208
The third...

09:41.208 --> 09:44.083
was this.

09:44.083 --> 09:44.959
Wow.

09:44.959 --> 09:47.083
Ah.

09:47.083 --> 09:49.125
That is some statement.

09:51.959 --> 09:54.834
Well,
good luck, then.

