his best year.

12:07.500 --> 12:09.708
Sitting with everyone
so they can equivocate

12:09.708 --> 12:12.041
and explain away what's already
been shown clearly

12:12.041 --> 12:13.417
seems inefficient.
Taylor, I know you come

12:13.417 --> 12:17.291
from analytics, and I know that
the numbers are where you live,

12:17.291 --> 12:19.417
but got to learn
the other piece, too.

12:19.417 --> 12:21.542
There's a small group
who can do the math.

12:21.542 --> 12:23.875
There's an even smaller group
who can explain it.

12:23.875 --> 12:25.542
