Nice!

37:13.875 --> 37:17.041
Rudy! Rudy! Rudy! Rudy!

37:17.041 --> 37:21.250
Rudy! Rudy! Rudy! Rudy! Rudy!

37:21.250 --> 37:24.708
I just now realized
what they're saying, Rudy...

37:24.708 --> 37:26.125
Rudy! Rudy! Rudy!
as in Rudy Ruettiger.

37:26.125 --> 37:28.708
Rudy! Rudy! Rudy! Rudy!

