51:41.000 --> 51:43.083
Hey,
what's going on?

51:43.083 --> 51:46.125
Where are you?

51:46.125 --> 51:47.875
I'm trying.

51:47.875 --> 51:51.583
I don't know, Bobby.

51:51.583 --> 51:54.834
I'm -- I'm really trying.

